INTERMINE

These Perl modules allow the creation of file in InterMine XML format, 
as well as directly querying the web API.


SEE ALSO

http://trac.flymine.org/wiki/ItemsAPIPerl

perldoc lib/InterMine/ItemFactory.pm

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

To make:
    sudo cpan -i XML::Parser::PerlSAX XML::Writer IO::String URI LWP::UserAgent
    perl Makefile.PL
    make

To run the tests: (optional)
    sudo cpan -i Test::XML Test::More Test::Exception
    make test

To install:
    make install   (or: sudo make install)


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for these modules with 
the perldoc command.

